section.def:
Commissioner
                (處長) means the Commissioner for Census and
            Statistics appointed under section 3;

undertaking
                (經營) means any undertaking whether by way of
            trade or business or otherwise;

subparagraph.content:
the persons, premises, establishments or other matters, in respect of
                        which particulars for the purpose of the census are to be
                        obtained;

specify the date or dates on which or the period in respect of which
                        the survey is to be carried
                        out;
